# Smart Mirror

## Overview
A smart IoT-based mirror that displays daily tasks, calendar events, and responds to user presence using sensors and cloud integration. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}

---

## Features
- Displays calendar/events
- Presence detection
- Cloud integration
- OLED display output

---

## Concepts
- Internet of Things (IoT)
- Cloud communication
- Sensor integration
- Event-driven programming

---

## Components
- ESP32 / ESP8266
- OLED Display
- Ultrasonic Sensor
- Wi-Fi Module

---

## Working
- Detects user presence
- Fetches data from cloud
- Displays on screen

---

## Applications
- Smart homes
- Personal assistants
- Daily planning systems

